quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  53,26,"Ana soni Achimalaika ŵalingwa kumawunde ŵangaŵa nkukamuchisya chondechonde jao chilichose, ikaŵeje panyuma pakupeleka lusa Allah kwa jwaankunsaka (mwa ŵanganyao kuti awombe duwa ja chondechonde), ni kunonyelwa najo (nkuwombeledwajo)"
  53,27,Chisimu aŵala ŵangakukulupilila ya Akhera akwakolanga Achimalaika ni mena gachikongwe (pakuŵecheta kuti ŵanganyao ŵanache ŵachikongwe ŵa Allah)
  53,28,"Ni nganakola ŵanganyao pa yalakweyo umanyilisi uliose, ngakukuya ikaŵeje liganichisya, sano liganichisya lyangakamuchisya chilichose pa yakuona"
  53,29,"Basi munnekaani ajula jwaachitundumalile chikumbusyo Chetu (Qur’an), ni ngajukusaka ikaŵeje umi wa duniya"
  53,30,"Chele ni chipelela chao cha umanyilisi. Chisimu Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) ni ŵaakummanyilila jwaapoteele kuleka litala Lyakwe, nambo soni ni ŵaakummanyilila jwajongweche"
  53,31,"Soni Allah ni Nsyene yosope yaili ku mawunde ni yaili petaka, kuti akaalipile aŵala ŵasakesye pa yaŵapanganyisye, ni kwalipila yambone aŵala ŵaakolosisye (masengo)"
  53,32,"Aŵala ŵaakuliŵambasya ilemwa yekulungwa-kulungwa, ni yakunyalaya, ikaŵeje yamwanamwana. Chisimu Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) ni Ŵachikululuko chakusapanguka. Ŵalakwe ni ŵaakummanya chenene jenumanja, kutandila paŵan’gumbaga kuumila mwitaka, ni pandema jankuŵaaga misigo mu itumbo ya achimama ŵenu. Basi ngasilliswejesyaga mwachimisyene, Jwalakwe ni Jwaakummanya chenene jwaali ni woga (wakun’jogopa Allah)"
  53,33,Ana mum’bweni (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ) ajula jwaagalawiche (kuleka kuunda malamusi ga Allah)
  53,34,Ni jutosile panandi (mu chipanje chakwe) kaneka ni kuleka (kutolako)
  53,35,"Ana kukwakwe kwana umanyilisi wakusisika, basi jwalakwe ni jukuiona (yanti chipanje chakwecho chichimale ligongo lyakutola)"
  53,36,Ana nganijusalilidwa yaili mu ikalakala ya Musa
  53,37,Ni Ibrahima ajula juŵakwanilisye (chilanga cha Allah)
  53,38,Yanti jwantwiichile nsigo (wasambi) ngasaja kutwichila nsigo (wasambi) wajwine
  53,39,Niyanti mundu nganijukola ikaŵeje yajupanganyisye
  53,40,Nambo soni kuti masengo gakwe gaachionedwa
  53,41,Kaneko ni tachilipidwa malipilo gakwana
  53,42,Ni yanti kwa Ambuje ŵenu (Allah) ni kuchipelela (kwakuwujila indu yosope)
  53,43,Ni yanti Jwalakwe (Allah) ni Jwaakutendekaasyaga kuseka ni Jwaakutendekasyaga soni kulila
  53,44,Ni yanti Jwalakwe (Allah) ni Jwaakupeleka chiwa ni Jwaakupeleka soni umi
  53,45,Ni yanti Jwalakwe (Allah) ni jwaagumbile mitundu jiŵili; chachilume ni chachikongwe
  53,46,Kuumila mu lindondwa (lya ulume) pati litajidwe (m’chiŵelechelo)
  53,47,Ni yanti kwa Jwalakwe (Allah) kwana guumba kwine (kwakwimusya ŵawe m’malembe)
  53,48,"Ni yanti Jwalakwe (Allah) ni Jwaakupeleka yakwanila (kuikamulichisya masengo), ni Jwaakupeleka soni yakusalasya"
  53,49,Ni yanti Jwalakwe (Allah) ni M’mbuje jwa ndondwa ja chilimila (jaŵajigalagatilaga ŵarabu ŵane)
  53,50,Ni yanti Jwalakwe (Allah) ni juŵajonasile achina Adi ŵandanda
  53,51,"Ni achina Samuda, ni nganansigasya (ata jumo)"
  53,52,"Kwisa soni ŵandu ŵa Nuhu kalakala, chisimu ŵanganyao ŵaliji ŵalupuso nnope, ni ŵakusumba mpika nnope (pa sambi)"
  53,53,Ni misi jakupitikusyidwa (ja ŵandu ŵa Lutwi) ŵajigwisyisye
  53,54,Ni yam’bunichiile (misijo) yayam’bunichiile (yaili ilagasyo ya sakalawe syelongo lyejoche ni moto wa Jahannama)
  53,55,Ana ni chapi mu chindimba cha Ambuje ŵenu (Allah mmwe amundu) cha nkuchikaichila (kuti mwine nganichiŵa Chakwe)
  53,56,Aju (Muhammadi ﷺ) ni nkutetela jumpepe mwa akutetela ŵandanda
  53,57,Chikusejelela chakusejelela (Kiyama jikuŵandichila)
  53,58,Pangali jwampaka achiunukule (kuti chimanyiche ndema jakwe jakwichila) jwangaŵaga Allah
  53,59,Ana jenumanja nkujisimonga aji abaliji (Qur’an)
  53,60,Ni nkuseka (mwachipongwe) ni ngalilaga (pati nchipikanaga yogoyo ya Allah)
  53,61,Ni n’gamba kwanjila pe
  53,62,Basi munsujudilaani Allah ni mun’galagatileje (Jwele Jikape)
  54,1,"Ndaŵi (jakwichila Kiyama) jiŵandichile, ni ugaanjiiche mwesi"
  54,2,"Soni naga ali achiweni chisimosimo akasanyosyaga, ni akutiji: “(Awu ni) usaŵi wakwendelechela.”"
  54,3,"Ni ŵaakaaniile, ni kuya isako yao, sano chindu chilichose (chambone kapena chakusakala chaŵapanganyisye mundu) chiŵele chakutamilichika (malipilo gakwe lisiku lya Kiyama)"
  54,4,Soni chisimu chene pamasile pasyaayiiche ŵanganyao ngani (mu aji Qur’an) syasikwete nkati mwakwe ikaanyo yaukali (yakwakanya kutenda yakusakala)
  54,5,"(Aji Qur’an jiŵele jegumbale) lunda lwakusokoka nnope, nambo itetelo ya akutetela nganiyiŵa ikamuchisye (kwa ŵandu ŵaajitundumalile)"
  54,6,Basi mwalekani. (Mwakumbusyani) lisiku lyatachiŵilanga nkuŵilanga (Israfil) ku chindu chakunyalaya kusyene (chiŵalanjilo cha pa Kiyama)
  54,7,"Gali gateteŵele meso gao, achikopokanganaga m’malembe, nti chisawu ŵanganyao sombe syakubalalikangana"
  54,8,"Achikangamalaga (aku ali anyakwile ngosi, mwanja) wa kwankuŵilanga. Achimakafili tachiti: “Ali ni lisiku lyakusausya kusyene.”"